+# Oracle Checkpoint
+
+Use this record only when deterministic evidence cannot resolve a review-critical question.
+Do not use it to bypass missing implementation or verification work.
+
+## Question
+
+- Unresolved question:
+- Why deterministic evidence is insufficient:
+
+## Evidence Inspected
+
+- `repo/path`: what was checked and what remained ambiguous
+
+## Decision
+
+- Outcome: approved | rejected | blocked | deferred
+- Rationale:
+
+## Owner
+
+- Decision owner:
+- Follow-up owner:
+
+## Next Action
+
+- Action:
+- Required before completion claim: yes | no
